snippet.title: Firewar - Update 1.0.0.5 (BETA)
snippet.description:
Whats New ?

- Improve Graphics Art to Get best experience
- New Preview Arena
- Improve Performance
- Fix Multiplayer

- Can Now UP Selected Soldier EXP while playing To Get more unlocked weapons & Cards
- Endless Level Bar Show When Go Next Level
- Fix Bugs

Game Available Now For Android

Google Play :
https://bit.ly/3tdD7dT
